{"kanda":6,"sarga":16,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"सुनिविष्टंहितंवाक्यमुक्तवन्तंविभीषणम् ।अब्रवीत्परुषंवाक्यंरावणःकालचोदितः","trans":"While Vibheeshana advised in Ravana's favour with all good intention, Ravana who was under the influence of death spoke harsh words.","words":[{"d":"सुनिविष्टम्","m":"with good intention"},{"d":"हितम्","m":"favourable"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उक्तवन्तम्","m":"that were spoken by"},{"d":"विभीषणं:","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"कालचोदितः","m":"influenced by death"},{"d":"परुषम्","m":"harsh"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"आब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"वसेत्सहसपत्नेनक्रुद्धेऽनाशीविषेणवा ।नतुमित्रप्रवादेनसंवसेच्छत्रुसेविना","trans":"\"One can live with a known enemy or even with an angry and venomous serpent but cannot stay together with one who professes to be a friend and devoted to an enemy.\"","words":[{"d":"सपत्नेनसह:","m":"with known enemy"},{"d":"वसेत्","m":"can live with"},{"d":"कृद्धेन:","m":"angry"},{"d":"अशीविषेणच:","m":"even with venomous serpent"},{"d":"मित्रप्रवादेन:","m":"professing to be a friend"},{"d":"शत्रुणासहतु:","m":"devoted to enemy"},{"d":"नसंवसेत्","m":"cannot stay together."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"जानामिशीलंज्ञातीनांसर्वलोकेषुराक्षस: ।हृष्यन्तिव्यसनेष्वेतेज्ञातीनाज्ञातयस्सदा","trans":"\"The behaviour of close relatives in all worlds is known to me. They are happy at the difficulties of relatives.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षस:","m":"O Rakshasa"},{"d":"सर्वलोकेषु:","m":"in all the worlds"},{"d":"ज्ञातीनाम्","m":"of close relatives"},{"d":"शीलम्","m":"behaviour"},{"d":"जानामि:","m":"is known to me"},{"d":"एते","m":"these"},{"d":"ज्ञातयः","m":"relatives"},{"d":"सदा:","m":"always"},{"d":"ज्ञातीनाम्","m":"of relatives"},{"d":"व्यसनेषु:","m":"when in difficulty"},{"d":"हृष्यन्ति:","m":"are happy."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"प्रथानंसाधनंवैद्यंधर्मशीलंचराक्षस: ।ज्ञातयोह्यवमन्यन्तेशूरंपरिभवन्तिच","trans":"\"O Rakshasa Relatives will insult and disapprove their chief even if he is an accomplished one, a virtuous one or a heroic one and does his duty (as a ruler).\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षस:","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"ज्ञातयः","m":"relatives"},{"d":"प्रथानम्","m":"chief"},{"d":"साधकम्","m":"accomplished वैद्यम्: learned ones"},{"d":"धर्मशीलंच:","m":"and one who is virtuous"},{"d":"शूरम्","m":"heroic ones"},{"d":"अवमन्यस्तेहि:","m":"will disapprove"},{"d":"परिभवन्तिच:","m":"will disrespect."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"नित्यमन्योन्यसम्हृष्टाव्यसनेष्वाततायिनः ।प्रच्छन्नहृदयाघोराज्ञातयस्तुभयावहाः","trans":"\"Pretending to be friendly forever the relatives rejoice in them is fortunes of their relatives. They create terrible fear like desperadoes and covertly ones.\"","words":[{"d":"व्यसनेषु:","m":"in misfortunes"},{"d":"नित्यम्","m":"forever"},{"d":"अन्योन्यसम्हृष्टाः","m":"rejoice pretending to be friendly"},{"d":"आततायिनः","m":"a desperado"},{"d":"प्रच्छन्नहृदयाः","m":"a covertly person"},{"d":"घोरा:","m":"terrible"},{"d":"ज्ञातियः","m":"relatives"},{"d":"भयावहाः","m":"create fear."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"श्रूयन्तेहस्तिभिर्गीताश्श्लोकाःपद्मवनेक्वचित् ।पाशहस्तान्नरान्द्रुष्टवाशृणुतान्गदतोमम","trans":"\"In the past elephants in the lotus park, uttered some verses on seeing men holding snares in hand. I will relate those that I heard. You may listen.\"","words":[{"d":"पुरा:","m":"in the past"},{"d":"पद्मवने:","m":"in the lotus park"},{"d":"पाशहस्तान्","m":"one holding the snares"},{"d":"नरान्","m":"men in hand"},{"d":"दृष्ट्वा:","m":"seeing"},{"d":"हस्तिभिः","m":"even elephants"},{"d":"गीताः","m":"uttered"},{"d":"श्लोकाः","m":"verses"},{"d":"श्रूयन्ते:","m":"heard of"},{"d":"गदतः","m":"relate"},{"d":"मम:","m":"to me"},{"d":"शृणु:","m":"listen."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"नाग्निर्नान्यानिशस्त्राणिननःपाशाभयावहाः ।घोरास्स्वार्थप्रयुक्तास्तुज्ञातयोनोभयावहाः","trans":"\"We have no fear of fire or weapons or noose of death. Selfish relatives are causing fear in us.\"","words":[{"d":"अग्नि:","m":"fire"},{"d":"न:","m":"no"},{"d":"अन्यानि:","m":"others"},{"d":"शस्त्राणि:","m":"weapons"},{"d":"न:","m":"no"},{"d":"पाशाः","m":"noose"},{"d":"भयावहाः","m":"fear"},{"d":"न:","m":"no"},{"d":"घोराः","m":"terrific"},{"d":"स्वार्थप्रयुक्ताः","m":"one who is selfish"},{"d":"ज्ञातयः","m":"close relatives"},{"d":"नः","m":"for us"},{"d":"भयावहाः","m":"causing fear."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"उपायमेतेवक्ष्यन्तिग्रहणेनात्रसंशयः ।कृत्स्नाद्भयाद् ज्ञातिभयंसुकष्टंविदितंचन","trans":"\"It is known that they (paternal relatives) teach the means to catch us. Out of all fears the fear of close relatives is the great difficulty for us.\"","words":[{"d":"एते:","m":"they"},{"d":"ग्रहणे:","m":"to catch"},{"d":"उपायम्","m":"means"},{"d":"वक्ष्यन्ति:","m":"teach"},{"d":"कृत्स्ना:","m":"great"},{"d":"भयात्","m":"fear"},{"d":"ज्ञातिभयम्","m":"fear of paternal relatives"},{"d":"नः","m":"for us"},{"d":"सुकष्टम्","m":"very difficult"},{"d":"विदितम्","m":"is known."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"विद्यतेगोषुसम्पन्नंविद्यतेब्राह्मणेदमः ।विद्यतेस्त्रीषुचापल्यंविद्यतेज्ञातितोभयम्","trans":"\"In the cows' wealth is present, in the brahmins forbearance is seen, in the women capriciousness exists but in close relatives fear is present.\"","words":[{"d":"गोषु:","m":"in cows"},{"d":"सम्पन्नम्","m":"wealth"},{"d":"विद्यते:","m":"is present"},{"d":"ज्ञातितः","m":"in close relatives"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"विद्यते:","m":"is seen"},{"d":"स्त्रीषु:","m":"in women"},{"d":"चापल्यम्","m":"capriciousness"},{"d":"विद्यते:","m":"is present"},{"d":"ब्राह्मणे:","m":"in brahmins"},{"d":"दमः","m":"forbearance"},{"d":"विद्यते:","m":"is present."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"ततोनेष्टमिदंसौम्ययदहंलोकसत्कृतः ।ऐश्वर्यमभिजातश्चज्ञातीनांमूर्ध्न्यवस्थितः","trans":"\"Gentle (Vibheeshana) one Since you belong to the same kinsfolk (as I) you do not like me, who is born of noble descent, attained the position of chief (of clan), is worshipped by the world, and attained sovereignty.\"","words":[{"d":"सौम्य:","m":"gentle"},{"d":"ततः","m":"therefore"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"लोकसत्कृतः","m":"worshipped by the people"},{"d":"ऐश्वर्यम्","m":"sovereignty"},{"d":"अभिजातःच:","m":"born of noble descent"},{"d":"ज्ञातीनाम्","m":"of the clan"},{"d":"मूध्नर्य:","m":"chief"},{"d":"अवस्थित:","m":"attained"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"नइष्टम्","m":"not like."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"यथापुष्करपत्रेषुपतितास्तोयबिन्दवः ।नश्लेषमभिगच्छन्तितथाऽनार्येषुसङ्गतम्","trans":"\"Just as drops of water that fall on lotus leaves do not adhere to each other, like wise however long you spend with an unworthy (relative) one, good friendship does not take place.\"","words":[{"d":"पुष्करपत्रेषु:","m":"on the lotus leaves"},{"d":"पतिताः","m":"fallen"},{"d":"तोयबिन्दवः","m":"drops of water"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"so also"},{"d":"श्लेषम्","m":"adhering to"},{"d":"न:","m":"not"},{"d":"अभिगच्छन्ति:","m":"however long you spend"},{"d":"अनार्येषु:","m":"with unworthy"},{"d":"सङ्गतम्","m":"good friendship"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"likewise."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"यथामधुकरस्तर्षाद्रसंविन्दन्नविद्यते ।तथात्वमपितत्रैवतथानार्येषुसौहृदम्","trans":"\"Just as honeybees do not have gratitude after drinking (honey) and satisfying, the friendship with an unworthy person like you is of no use.\"","words":[{"d":"यथा:","m":"that way"},{"d":"रसम्","m":"juice"},{"d":"विन्दन्","m":"gaining"},{"d":"मधुकरः","m":"honeybees"},{"d":"तर्षात्","m":"satisfying"},{"d":"नविद्यते:","m":"does not know"},{"d":"त्वमपि:","m":"you also"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"likewise"},{"d":"तत्रैवअनार्येषु:","m":"in the same way with unworthy ones"},{"d":"सौहृदम्","m":"making friendship"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"that way."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"यथापूर्वंगजस्स्नात्वागृह्यहस्तेनवैरजः ।दूषयत्यात्मनोदेहंतथानार्येषुसङ्गतम्","trans":"\"Just as an elephant takes dust with its trunk and abuses (and spreads on) its own body after taking a bath so also is the association with unworthy ones.\"","words":[{"d":"गजः","m":"elephant"},{"d":"पूर्वम्","m":"first"},{"d":"स्नात्वा:","m":"taking bath"},{"d":"हस्तेन:","m":"with its own trunk"},{"d":"रजः","m":"dust,गृह्य: taking"},{"d":"आत्मनः","m":"own"},{"d":"देहम्","m":"body"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"in the sa